through and through.

16:10.625 --> 16:12.166
- You?
- Immigrant

16:12.166 --> 16:14.458
from distant shores--
Oak Brook.

16:14.458 --> 16:15.083
That's nice.

16:15.083 --> 16:16.834
What brings you down here

16:16.834 --> 16:18.458
