of dance partners.

16:26.291 --> 16:28.458
So have you met
any of the other tenants yet?

16:28.458 --> 16:29.125
No.

16:29.125 --> 16:31.250
Well, the old lady with cancer

16:31.250 --> 16:33.583
and cats has been living in 1C

16:33.583 --> 16:35.208
since the South seceded
from the Union.

16:35.208 --> 16:38.083
