move in here yourself

16:56.959 --> 16:59.041
or rent this one out?

16:59.667 --> 17:02.542
Gonna rent it.

17:02.542 --> 17:04.583
How much?

17:04.583 --> 17:06.375
Not sure.
Area's up and comin'.

17:06.375 --> 17:08.583
Urban homesteaders
and all that.

17:08.583 --> 17:13.000
Yeah. Lincoln Square lumberjacks
are definitely migrating south.

17:15.959 --> 17:18.834
I'm not--
I'm not gay.

17:18.834 --> 17:20.667
Oh, cool, I'm not looking.

17:20.667 --> 17:22.834
And you're not my type anyway.

17:22.834 --> 17:24.166
- What's your type?
- Blonde and bitchy.

17:24.166 --> 17:26.917
I'm a masochist--
not physical pain,

17:26.917 --> 17:29.333
but emotional turmoil
is my thing.

17:29.333 --> 17:31.291
- [chuckles]
- [Mel] Jesus, Nessa.

17:31.291 --> 17:34.041
What the hell
is taking so long?

17:34.041 --> 17:36.250
We were supposed to be there,
like, ten minutes ago.

17:36.250 --> 17:38.792
Mel, our new landlady,
Fiona.

17:38.792 --> 17:40.542
Fiona's an endangered species.

17:40.542 --> 17:44.041
- Genuine South Side.
- [both laugh]

17:44.041 --> 17:46.000
