working that corner.

19:00.667 --> 19:02.458
- Nah, I got a new boyfriend.
- [Ian] Oh.

19:02.458 --> 19:04.709
Hey.

19:05.291 --> 19:07.125
Maybe I should take 20.

19:07.125 --> 19:09.792
Hey, don't get greedy,
all right?

19:10.625 --> 19:11.792
Hey.

19:12.917 --> 19:14.542
Hey!

19:14.542 --> 19:17.125
The city giving you free condoms
to distribute now?

19:17.125 --> 19:18.792
No, he buys them himself.

19:18.792 --> 19:20.000
He's gonna go broke
trying to sheathe

19:20.000 --> 19:22.375
South Side Chicago's
teenage libido

19:22.375 --> 19:24.291
in lubricated latex.

19:24.291 --> 19:25.792
No, I shoplift them mostly.

19:25.792 --> 19:28.250
- [laughter]
- No, he doesn't.

19:30.208 --> 19:33.166
Hey, I'm heading to happy hour
at Jeffrey's after work.

19:33.166 --> 19:33.917
You busy?

19:33.917 --> 19:35.375
