20:40.208 --> 20:43.208
Lost ticket pays
full price, sir.

20:43.208 --> 20:44.709
$24, please.

20:44.709 --> 20:47.291
I'm not giving you $24.

20:47.291 --> 20:50.208
We take Visa, Mastercard,
and American Express.

20:50.208 --> 20:52.291
I came in ten minutes ago,
right there beside you.

20:52.291 --> 20:55.208
- You didn't see me?
- No, sir.

20:55.208 --> 20:57.917
My job requires that I focus
on the exiting vehicles.

20:57.917 --> 21:00.291
Have you tried
retracing your steps,

21:00.291 --> 21:01.333
see if you can find where you
may have lost your ticket?

21:01.333 --> 21:03.291
I'm not retracing anything,
bitch.

21:03.291 --> 21:04.834
Take the goddamn money.

21:04.834 --> 21:06.667
Please watch
your language, sir.

21:06.667 --> 21:08.041
My language?

21:08.041 --> 21:09.166
You want me to get out
of this truck

21:09.166 --> 21:11.208
and fuck you up?

21:11.208 --> 21:13.583
No, sir. I don't.

21:13.583 --> 21:15.542
Because if you were
to get out of your truck,

21:15.542 --> 21:17.333
I would have to Tase you

21:17.333 --> 21:18.750
and then superglue
your mouth and eyelids shut

21:18.750 --> 21:19.250
until the police arrive.

21:19.250 --> 21:22.291
[Taser crackling]

21:23.250 --> 21:24.041
Now, will that be cash
or credit, sir?

21:24.041 --> 21:26.208
