- For what?

24:50.291 --> 24:51.875
One-bedroom apartment.

24:51.875 --> 24:52.792
From that dump
you just bought?

24:52.792 --> 24:55.959
- No. Five hundred, tops.
- Five hundred?

24:55.959 --> 24:57.542
Jesus.

24:57.542 --> 25:00.000
- All right, I gotta go to work.
- No BJs, Kev.

25:00.000 --> 25:03.625
