and nothing below the waist.

25:03.625 --> 25:04.834
V, we could really use
the money.

25:04.834 --> 25:07.291
No.

25:07.291 --> 25:09.500
Five hundred? Really?

25:09.500 --> 25:11.166
Kev doesn't know
what he's talking about.

25:11.166 --> 25:11.834
