you got today?

25:45.792 --> 25:47.083
Strawberry and lime.

25:47.083 --> 25:47.583
Two of each.
Extra whipped cream.

25:47.583 --> 25:49.208
[chuckles]
Okay.

25:58.792 --> 26:01.291
