26:02.583 --> 26:03.834
You just got sober.

26:03.834 --> 26:05.208
Yeah, well, we're friends.

26:05.208 --> 26:06.291
I call bullshit.

26:06.291 --> 26:09.208
No new relationships.

26:09.208 --> 26:11.333
Yeah, it's not new.

26:11.333 --> 26:14.208
She broke up with you
because of your drinking.

26:14.208 --> 26:16.250
If you really think
she's the one,

26:16.250 --> 26:18.792
just tell her you need
six months to work the steps.

26:18.792 --> 26:20.542
All right, six months, huh?

26:20.542 --> 26:22.250
