work the steps,

26:22.250 --> 26:23.792
you're gonna fuck it up
and drink

26:23.792 --> 26:25.834
next time
you guys are in a fight.

26:36.083 --> 26:36.750
I'm gonna ask for 850.

26:36.750 --> 26:39.000
