V, you're on the register.

27:03.917 --> 27:06.750
Lip, Sierra,
looks like we're cooking.

27:06.750 --> 27:08.875
♪ Flesh, blood,
skin, and bone ♪

27:08.875 --> 27:12.667
♪ Drag me down
