27:13.667 --> 27:16.667
- I'd like to apologize, son.
- For what?

27:16.667 --> 27:19.291
For whatever I've done to you
that I can't remember.

27:19.291 --> 27:21.667
What do you remember?

27:21.667 --> 27:23.959
Um, honestly, not much.

27:23.959 --> 27:27.041
I'm making amends
to all the people I've harmed

27:27.041 --> 27:28.458
the three decades
your mother had me

27:28.458 --> 27:30.875
under her intoxicating spell.

27:30.875 --> 27:31.792
So is there anything
that you can think of

27:31.792 --> 27:34.709
that I should apologize
to you for?

27:34.709 --> 27:36.291
Kind of a long list.

27:36.291 --> 27:38.333
Well, let me just apologize...

27:38.333 --> 27:40.750
for all of it, huh?

27:42.333 --> 27:44.792
I'm sorry, son.

27:46.291 --> 27:49.250
Thank you.
Okay.

27:49.250 --> 27:51.208
I'm off to find others
in need of my amends.

27:51.208 --> 27:53.166
I made a list.

27:53.166 --> 27:54.583
That's it?

27:54.583 --> 27:57.417
No, it's just the beginning.

27:57.417 --> 28:00.458
Once I begin making amends
for the things I do remember,

28:00.458 --> 28:03.125
it'll jog my memory
for all the rest.

28:03.125 --> 28:05.166
